            <br />
            <p>Surat is a city located in Gujarat in India. It is also known as Diamond hub.
               Surat is also know for its textile market.</p>
            <br />
            <br />
            <img src="E:\\MCDA\\vs react\\Project1\\Project1\\weather.png" /><br />
            <p>- &deg;C</p>
        </div>
    );
  }
}
